data.description: Step inside and you'll find a spacious layout, boasting 4 bedrooms and an office for all your professional needs. Hosting formal gatherings? Our formal dining area is the perfect setting for creating unforgettable memories. And let's not forget our butler's pantry, a convenient addition for all your culinary adventures. The den, generously sized, can be transformed into a multi-functional space - imagine it as your very own office retreat, a media room for family movie nights, a game room for endless fun, or even a vibrant bar/hangout spot. Quality is guaranteed, as this home is in pristine condition and only 4 years old. Marvel at the custom fireplace, mature oak trees, and luxurious custom oversized doors. Parking will never be an issue with an oversized 3-car garage to accommodate all your vehicles. Situated on a lush and manicured acre tract, this home provides the perfect escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. This home also backs up to River Ranch Park, a quiet 1300 acre park for equestrian, camping, hiking, and bicycling. You are also, it's just a quick distance to downtown Liberty Hill or Leander, ensuring you have access to all the amenities you need.
